      <title>中方敦促美方停止“无理打压”TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-urges-us-to-stop-unreasonably-suppressing-tiktok</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国呼吁美国停止“无理打压”TikTok，因为这款拥有 1.7 亿美国人使用的应用程序已成为超级大国之间持续紧张关系的中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-urges-us-to-stop-unreasonably-suppressing-tiktok</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
